#Text=The Philadelphia 76ers defeated the Charlotte Hornets , 110 - 99 , at Wells Fargo Center on Friday evening .

#Text=The 76ers ( 34 - 27 ) looked like clear - cut favorites coming in , as the combination of their 19 - 10 home mark and the visitors ' 10 - 19 road record seemed to give a clear edge to the hosts on paper .
#Text=However just as the two tallies were diametric opposites , the first half fittingly played out quite unexpectedly as well .
#Text=The Hornets ( 28 - 35 ) managed to forge a 56 - 48 halftime advantage based on some solid all - around play .
#Text=However , Philadelphia started chipping away in the third , making a slight dent in their deficit before dominating in the final 12 minutes .
#Text=The home squad would go on to put 36 up on the scoreboard in the fourth period , their best quarterly total of the contest by far .
#Text=Their play was just as impressive on the other side of the ball , as they limited the Hornets to a stingy 19 points to seal the comeback win .
#Text=Locked-in shooting was key to the victory , as Charlotte posted a 51 percent success rate from the field .
#Text=Kemba Walker led the way for the Hornets with 31 points , a total he supplemented with five assists , one rebound and one steal .
#Text=Frank Kaminsky provided a bench - leading 19 points and added four rebounds and three assists .
#Text=Nicolas Batum supplied 14 points , 13 rebounds , eight assists and one steal .
#Text=Michael Kidd-Gilchrist returned from injury to register nine points , one rebound , one assist and one steal .
#Text=Dwight Howard had an unusually quiet game while dealing with Joel Embiid , mustering just six points , six rebounds and two assists .
#Text=Embiid paced the Sixers with a 23 - point , 14 - rebound double - double that also included four assists and three blocks .
#Text=J.J.
#Text=Redick poured in 18 points and added two rebounds and two assists .
#Text=Ersan Ilyasova matched Redick 's scoring total to lead the bench and also delivered four boards and three assists .
#Text=Robert Covington turned in 16 points , five rebounds , three assists and three steals .
#Text=Ben Simmons ' line consisted of 15 points , eight boards , six assists and one block .
#Text=Dario Saric rounded out a productive night for the starting five by generating nine points , seven rebounds and six assists .
#Text=The Hornets remain on the road and next visit the Toronto Raptors on Sunday evening , while the Sixers visit the Milwaukee Bucks on Sunday night as well .
